*xephem-3.6.2 (23 Dec 2004)

  23 Dec 2004; Olivier Fisette <ribosome@gentoo.org> +metadata.xml,
  +xephem-3.6.2-r1.ebuild, +xephem-3.6.2.ebuild:
  Moved from app-sci/xephem to sci-astronomy/xephem.

*xephem-3.6.2-r1 (23 Dec 2004)

  23 Dec 2004; Patrick Kursawe <phosphan@gentoo.org> +xephem-3.6.2-r1.ebuild:
  Now installing data into /usr/share/xephem where they belong.
  No longer adding -ffast-math.
  Installing a few directories that the old ebuild didn't get.

  21 Dec 2004; Patrick Kursawe <phosphan@gentoo.org> -xephem-3.5.2.ebuild,
  -xephem-3.6.1.ebuild, xephem-3.6.2.ebuild, -xephem-3.6.ebuild:
  Big cleanup. Removing fetch restriction after getting mirror permission from
  the developers.

  20 Dec 2004; Patrick Kursawe <phosphan@gentoo.org> xephem-3.6.2.ebuild:
  Declaring latest version stable because the package has fetch restriction and
  older versions aren't available for download any more.

